2026-05-16T20:14:18.9560747Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9561238Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9561595Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9561939Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9562293Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9562631Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
