2026-05-16T20:14:18.9829859Z 271            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9830238Z 272            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9830602Z 273            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9830989Z 274            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9831224Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9831634Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9832016Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9832371Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9833029Z 279            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-16T20:14:18.9833258Z 280            preserve via tools:node="merge".
